<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038469" n="159v"/>
<p>Putabam me in duabus ultimis ad Te datis <rs key="B_991170517054105501 B_991170517054005501" type="letter">literis</rs> mentem meam
                    <lb/>tam clare expressisse, ut non posses <add>de aliquibus dubitare aut</add> verba mea accipere in se<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quiorem sensum, sed me tam felicem non fuisse ex <rs key="B_991170517053805501" type="letter">iis</rs> didici,
                    <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <date when="1718-06-27">nupero die 27. pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>teriti mensis</date> respondisti. Dolorem quem
                    <lb/>exinde concipio auget difficultas, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> obstat, quominus ad
                    <lb/>singula qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stionum tuarum capita pro voto tuo respondere
                    <lb/>possim. Tot enim ambiguitatibus (pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipue circa conditiones
                    <pb facs="1038470" n="159r"/>
<lb/><hi rend="u">datas</hi>) implicit<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sunt ill<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stiones, ut<del> vix</del> putem, me<del> illas</del>
<lb/>difficulter illas scripto expediturum esse. Constitui sub finem <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tis, <subst><del>cum</del><add>postquam</add></subst> calor <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>qui <rs key="place_VER-repven" type="place">Venetiis</rs> major quam hic esse perhibetur<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> defer<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>buerit, ire <rs key="place_VER-repven" type="place">Venetias</rs> et (si permittes, ut sine impensis tuis id fiat)
                    <lb/>venire in domum tuam, ubi viva voce melius quam scriptis de
                    <lb/>his rebus disseremus. Interim si tamdiu expectare non possis, si
                    <lb/>placet, singulis epistolis singulas qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stiones ventilabimus; eum autem
                    <lb/>in finem oportet, ut <hi rend="u">conditiones datas</hi> et omnes Problematum circum<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>stantias distincte mihi exponas. <abbr>Ex. gr.</abbr> ultima, quam mihi in <rs key="B_991170517054005501" type="letter">episto<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>la</rs>tua proponis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stio h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c est <cit type="long"><quote><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>annon velocitas sanguinis aut
                    <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice><figure facs="../images/figures/1038470_01.png" hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"><figDesc>Darstellung eines verzweigten Blutgef√§sses.</figDesc></figure>fluidi progredientis ab <formula>A</formula> ad <formula>D</formula> motu vel uniformi vel
                    <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>quocunque modo variabili sit minor in ramo <formula>BC</formula> angustio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>re quam sit truncus <formula>ABD</formula> et angulum acutum <formula>CBD</formula> ad
                    <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>partes motus constituente cum trunco <formula>ABD</formula>.<choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice></quote></cit> Ad hanc qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nem nunquam respondere potero nisi mihi dicas, quid moveat Sangui<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nem per truncum et per ramum, quomodo moveat, quamdiu moveat,
                    <lb/>et quo in statu sit<del> s</del> truncus et ramus ante<del>quam sanguis per illos</del> <add>illud<del> temporis</del> temporis</add>
<lb/><subst><del>moveatur</del><add>momentum de quo qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stio instituitur</add></subst>, item quid intelligas per velocitatem (nam et hoc rogan<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>di justas habeo causas) ut <unclear>t</unclear>aceam de figura et situ ipsorum cana<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lium, prout enim vari<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fiunt hypotheses, tum aliqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tum omnes
                    <lb/>harum rer<unclear>um</unclear> not<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> esse debent. Ne autem prorsus sterilis sit
                    <lb/>h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c mea epistola, respondebo hac vice ad difficultates quas movisti
                    <lb/>circa ea qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> dixi de motu fluidi per <rs type="keyword">canalem plicatum</rs> et de
                    <lb/>comparatione motus sanguinis cum motu aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> effluentis ex
                    <lb/>clepsydra. Petis explicationem et demonstrationem hujus propo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sitionis, quod (in hypothesi decrementum velocitatis
                    <pb facs="1038471" n="160r"/>
<lb/>in plica aliqua factum esse proportionale ipsi velocitati) velo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>citas fluidi per ultimum ramum <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>Tu posuisti <hi rend="u">plicam</hi> loco <hi rend="u">rami</hi><choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> 
                    <lb/>exeuntis sit ad velocitatem fluidi per primum ramum in ratio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ne totuplicata rationis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> est inter velocitatem fluidi per
                    <lb/>secundum ramum et inter velocitatem ejus per primum ra<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mum, quot sunt unitates in numero plicarum. Ego utrumque
                    <lb/>horum pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stiti in <rs type="letter" key="B_991170517054105501">epistola</rs> mea penultima, exemplo adducto
                    <lb/>canaliculi habentis 4 ramos sive 3 plicas, quod si attente
                    <lb/>perpendisses, sine dubio mentem meam percepisses. Phrasis
                    <lb/>illa qua Tu uteris ... in ratione composita .... toties multipli<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cata ... nullum rectum habe<del>n</del>t sensum, ut autem recte per<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cipias, quid per <hi rend="u">rationem totuplicatam</hi> intellexerim, rem
                    <lb/>exemplo declarabo. Si sit ratio aliqua <abbr>ex. gr.</abbr> 3 ad 2, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                    <lb/>ratio hoc modo exprimatur <formula>3 : 2</formula>, hujus rationis ratio dupli<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cata est ratio <formula>9 : 4</formula>, nempe ratio quadratorum numerorum 3
                    <lb/>et 2; ejusdem rationis <formula>3 : 2</formula> ratio triplicata est ratio <formula>27 : 8</formula> nem<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pe ratio cuborum numerorum 3 et 2; et sic generaliter ratio
                    <lb/>totuplicata rationis <formula>3 : 2</formula> quot sunt unitates in dato aliquo
                    <lb/>numero <formula>n</formula>, est ratio <formula>3^{n} : 2^{n}</formula>. Adeoque si velocitas per primum
                    <lb/>ramum vocetur <formula>a</formula>, velocitas per sedundum ramum vocetur <formula>b</formula>,
                    <lb/>velocitas per ultimum ramum <formula>x</formula>, et numerus<del> ramoru</del> plicar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">≈´</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
                    <lb/><formula>n</formula>, sive numerus ramorum <formula>n+1</formula>, sensus me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> propositionis erit
                    <lb/>hic, quod <formula>x . a :: b^{n} . a^{n}</formula> <abbr>h. e.</abbr> <formula>x=\frac{b^{n}}{a^{n-1}}</formula>; ejus autem demon<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>stratio facilis est, nam quia decrementum velocitatis in sin<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gulis plicis proportionale est velocitati cum qua fluidum
                    <pb facs="1038472" n="160v"/>
<lb/>appellit ad illam plicam (per <abbr>hypoth.</abbr>) erunt velocitates
                    <lb/>per singulos ramos in progressione geometrica sequente
                    <lb/><formula>a,b,\frac{bb}{a},\frac{b^{3}}{aa},\frac{b^{4}}{a^{3}},\frac{b^{5}}{a^{4}}</formula> <abbr><choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>c<supplied>.</supplied></abbr> et decrementa velocitatum
                    <lb/><del>respective </del><formula>a-b, b-\frac{bb}{a}, \frac{bb}{a}-\frac{b^{3}}{aa}, \frac{b^{3}}{aa}-\frac{b^{4}}{a^{3}}</formula> <abbr><choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>c.</abbr> in eadem nem<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pe<del>r</del> ratione respective cum suis velocitatibus integris pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gredientia. Ceterum recte dicis quod posito <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>ex mente <rs key="pers_DE-588-117584363" type="person">Bel<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lini</rs> et <rs key="pers_DE-588-117659606" type="person">Cheyn<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>i</rs><choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> velocitas fluidi per canaliculum 4800 pli<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>carum <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>accuratius dixisses <hi rend="u">ramorum</hi><choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> in exitu sit 1, et velo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>citas in introitu sit 4800, velocitas amissa sit 4799, sed
                    <lb/>Tibi ipsi contradicis falsam consequentiam hinc eliciendo et
                    <lb/>dicendo <cit><quote>"qua ratione ergo possumus asserere velocitatem in 
                    <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>singulis plicis amitti qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sit <formula>\frac{1}{4800}</formula> <hi rend="u">totius velocitatis</hi> <abbr><choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>c.</abbr><supplied>"</supplied></quote></cit>
<lb/>erras in hoc quod in sequentibus pro ista <hi rend="u">tota velocitate</hi> su<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mis unitatem, loco quod debuisses sumere 4800 qui numerus
                    <lb/>respondet velocitati prim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> integr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, nam in singulis plicis
                    <lb/>non amittitur <formula>\frac{1}{4800}</formula> unitatis, sed ami<subst><del>ttit</del><add>ssa</add></subst> velocitas<del> est</del> in una<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>qu<unclear>a</unclear>que plica est <formula>=\frac{1}{4800}\times 4800=1</formula>, adeo ut si numerus
                    <lb/>plicarum ponatur esse <formula>4799</formula> velocitas omnis amissa futu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ra sit <formula>=4799</formula>, adeoque velocitas in exitu <formula>= 1</formula>; quod si ve<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ro numerus plicarum ponatur esse <formula>4800</formula>, <subst><del>id</del><add>o</add></subst>mnis velocitas a<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mittetur, et velocitas in exitu tunc erit nulla; id quod so<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lum potest ostendere absurditatem opinionis <rs key="pers_DE-588-117584363" type="person">Bellinian<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> et
                    <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-117659606" type="person">Cheynean<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>. Venio nunc ad comparationem motus sanguinis
                    <pb facs="1038473" n="161r"/>
<lb/>cum motu aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ex clepsydra effluentis, circa quam comparatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nem Tu mentem meam nequaquam percepisti; si denuo perleges 
                    <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> hac de re dixi, invenies me non ipsum Cor repr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentasse
                    <lb/><subst><del>cum</del><add>per</add></subst> Clepsydr<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ƒÅ</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> (<del>id quod ineptum </del>quam comparationem
                    <lb/>tanquam ineptam ego studiose evitavi) sed me comparasse
                    <lb/>tantum vim <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">√†</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> contractione cordis oriundam cum vi qua
                    <lb/>aqua ex clepsydra effluens <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">√†</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> pondere superincumbentis
